amai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845280/extras/595d65981a3cdeae2bd4cbb2647349e0.poster.avif?t=1645203165\" width=608 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845280/extras/595d65981a3cdeae2bd4cbb2647349e0.webm?t=1645203165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845280/extras/595d65981a3cdeae2bd4cbb2647349e0.mp4?t=1645203165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Find items to crack chests!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845280/extras/10975e6a9c2ef3815659ccca8564f146.poster.avif?t=1645203165\" width=520 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845280/extras/10975e6a9c2ef3815659ccca8564f146.webm?t=1645203165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845280/extras/10975e6a9c2ef3815659ccca8564f146.mp4?t=1645203165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Try to survive at all costs and escape from this horror!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845280/extras/8ee51c46ca8067d6e91cc997a1a2c904.poster.avif?t=1645203165\" width=672 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845280/extras/8ee51c46ca8067d6e91cc997a1a2c904.webm?t=1645203165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845280/extras/8ee51c46ca8067d6e91cc997a1a2c904.mp4?t=1645203165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br>Game Features:<br>*Great graphics!<br>*Challenging puzzles!<br>*Awesome plot!<br>*Easter eggs!",
